## 3. Permanent Notes â€” Zettelkasten Specification

### 3.1 Atomicity Criteria

Each permanent note MUST:

1. **Contain exactly ONE idea** â€” indivisible into meaningful sub-concepts
2. **Be self-contained** â€” understandable without requiring other notes
3. **Have a declarative title** â€” expresses the complete idea in Subject-Verb-Object format
4. **Be 200â€“300 words** â€” concise and dense
5. **Be testable** â€” the concept can be verified, demonstrated, or applied

